{"tid":481220,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我用鼻噴左舊肉碎落男朋友舅父塊臉到","createTime":"2017-11-27T03:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-27T23:29:04.000Z","uid":90123,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5cf98e2ddfc74b6abad04c9cf3a70260465c395a","tid":481220,"uid":90123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T03:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n琴晚上男朋友屋企食飯，除左男朋友媽媽之外仲有佢舅父同舅母。<br />\n咁男朋友就坐我隔離，佢舅父坐左我對面。<br />\n都食得幾開心啦有講有笑咁。<br />\n<br />\n點知我食舊豬肉個時比佢地屋企隻貓嚇一嚇，舊肉入撚左鼻道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要好痕好想打乞次噴出黎，我已經極速望周圍有冇紙巾。<br />\n<br />\n點知都係一野噴左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n噴左舊肉落男朋友舅父塊臉上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有小小我啲鼻涕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後佢舅父話唔緊要，洗一洗臉繼續食，但我好想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以後仲上唔上去好？"},{"pid":"b19706b6fc9297bfb43014da8c2f604a41c5c258","tid":481220,"uid":78622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T03:37:17.000Z","msg":"仲係VISA單男朋友？"},{"pid":"a2c056c91694b229b9b1f76edca1f5cb466a9b77","tid":481220,"uid":136386,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T03:37:19.000Z","msg":"比佢噴返一q 打和 super<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd53bdf70acedf89890f5b8237bfc72cb95c44f","tid":481220,"uid":77622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T03:54:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲係VISA單男朋友？</blockquote><br />\n同問"},{"pid":"10292d88cc3962bdc7288194705cb8db1bd4c3a3","tid":481220,"uid":90123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T04:28:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲係VISA單男朋友？</blockquote><br />\n同問</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近幸褔快樂"},{"pid":"f60ec1cf479ac18cae05b4b135f578713bc10027","tid":481220,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T04:30:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08bce59585894f18c3f81d6931b905912deaed00","tid":481220,"uid":78622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:42:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲係VISA單男朋友？</blockquote><br />\n同問</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近幸褔快樂</blockquote><br />\n笑"},{"pid":"4712668992fd3ea884bad87dad30697a1693d19f","tid":481220,"uid":9726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:50:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86b508c9611430831efbe47fe6baa66e0b9e1763","tid":481220,"uid":50162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:55:07.000Z","msg":"屌你真係好嘔心，成隻豬咁"},{"pid":"1e25390db68933ac446c17cbff65bd0901e49a60","tid":481220,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:56:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你真係好嘔心，成隻豬咁</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f764804f92b725a78bf539a9b20a1603915fd14","tid":481220,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T23:08:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你真係好嘔心，成隻豬咁</blockquote><br />\n我都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d738974634bd308483b4ab931c7fa2a1e37f339c","tid":481220,"uid":53421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T23:29:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你真係好嘔心，成隻豬咁</blockquote><br />\n我都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n臭雞"}]}